Gerege Template AI v1.0
============================

Co-developed by / Хамтран бүтээсэн:
  - Gerege Systems Development Team
  - Claude AI (Anthropic)

2026

Derived from open-source work / Нээлттэй эх дээр суурилсан:
  - snykk/go-rest-boilerplate — Moh. Najib Fikri (MIT)
      https://github.com/snykk/go-rest-boilerplate
      Base architecture, JWT/OTP auth, mailer, audit, cache, observability, tests.
  - rachmanzz/fiber-starter — rachmanzz (MIT)
      https://github.com/rachmanzz/fiber-starter
      Fiber v3 idiom reference.

Changes from upstream / Эх төслөөс хийсэн өөрчлөлт:
  - HTTP layer: Gin -> Fiber v3
  - Data layer: sqlx -> GORM

